<h3>{{ _('OctoPiBox Configuration') }}</h3>
<p>Use this to automatically manage the two power outlets on the OctoPiBox. If enabled the power outlets will be automatically powered off after a print has completed succesfully. The time from print complete to power-off is configured using the power-off delay.</p>
<form class="form-horizontal">

	<div class="control-group">
		<div class="controls" title="{{ _('Check to enable automatic printer-off.') }}">
			<label class="checkbox">
				<input type="checkbox" data-bind="checked: settings.plugins.octopibox.enabled" /> {{ _('Check to enable automatic power-off to your OctoPiBox connected printer.') }}
			</label>
		</div>
	</div>
