		<div class="controls" title="{{ _('Check to enable automatic connections.') }}">
			<label class="checkbox">
				<input type="checkbox" data-bind="checked: settings.plugins.octopibox.auto_connect_enabled" /> {{ _('Check to automatically connect/disconnect with printer power-on/off.') }}
			</label>
		</div>
	</div> -->

	<div class="control-group" title="{{ _('Delay in seconds range 60 to 1800 (default 600).') }}">
		<label class="control-label">{{ _('Power-off delay') }}</label>
		<div class="controls">
			<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.timer_seconds">
		</div>
	</div>

	<h4>Power Pins</h4>
	<p>Set the Raspberry Pi GPIO pins that will be used to control the two OctoPiBox power outlets. BCM pin numbering is used.</p>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Printer power pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Printer pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.printer_pin">
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Spare power pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Spare pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.spare_pin">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<h4>Button Pins</h4>
	<p>Set the Raspberry Pi GPIO pins that will be used to control the two OctoPiBox power buttons.
		BCM pin numbering is used. Setting a button's enable pin to a value other than 0 will enable a printing interlock.
		The printing interlock will disable the power button to during printing to prevent accidental power-offs.
		The default is to enable printing interlock for the printer power button but not the spare power button.</p>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Button debounce in milliseconds.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Button debounce (ms)') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.button_debounce">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<h5>Printer Power Button</h5>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Printer power button pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Button pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.printer_button_pin">
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Button enable pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Button Enable pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.printer_button_enable_pin">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<h5>Spare Power Button</h5>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Spare power button pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Button pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.spare_button_pin">
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="control-group span5" title="{{ _('Spare power button enable pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Button Enable pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.spare_button_enable_pin">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h4>OctoPrint Status Light</h4>
	<p>Set the Raspberry Pi GPIO pins to use for the RGB LED used to indicate the current status of OctoPrint.</p>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="control-group span4" title="{{ _('Spare power button enable pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Red pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.status_red_pin">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="control-group span4" title="{{ _('Spare power button enable pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Green pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.status_green_pin">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="control-group span4" title="{{ _('Spare power button enable pin on the RaspberryPi. BCM number.') }}">
			<label class="control-label">{{ _('Blue pin') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.octopibox.status_blue_pin">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</form>
